Sprott Inc. (“Sprott”) is an alternative asset manager with a long track record of innovation and a focus on providing our clients with highly differentiated alternative investment strategies. Sprott has a corporate history dating back to 1981 and the company is internationally recognized for its resource investment expertise.
Headquartered in Toronto, Canada, Sprott also has offices in Calgary, Vancouver, New York, California and Hong Kong. The company operates through three primary lines of business:

Exchange Listed Products
Alternative Asset Management
Private Resource Investments

Sprott currently has approximately $9.7 billion in assets under management, approximately $7 billion of which is invested in the natural resource sector.









