Sprott Inc.


            
            Sprott, Inc. operates as an independent asset manager, which offers investment management services and investment advisory services. The company offers diverse range of products and investment strategies to its clients. It engages in asset management, physical bullion, private equity, and debt and wealth management businesses. Its history roots back to 1981. The company was founded by Eric Steven Sprott on February 13, 2008 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.

            
